        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I would like a family with a man and 2 children.</p>
                <p>I will works in a Company clothes with my friends.</p>
                <p>I would cheap a big house with jaccuzi, sauna and pool</p>
                <p>I would work just 10 year.</p>
                <p>I would go in Maldives for my holidays and I would live in Morocco.</p>
                <p>I love this land.</p>
                <p>I would go with my familie and my friend</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
